snippet.textDisplay: The OnePlus 7T Pro did come to the US, just in a shitty way, TMobile is the main seller of it but I ended up paying a little more to get an unlocked one from Amazon because I don't want to be limited by TMobile. Great phone, favorite thing is the battery, even with the bigger 90Hz screen it lasts at least 2-3x longer than my old OnePlus 6T McL and I can easily skip a day of charge if I have to.
